data.description: Stunning and just like new with all the bells and whistles you want in a home and on a corner lot. The secluded neighborhood offers you a great location for the commuter and for the person looking for the convenience of shopping, restaurants, and schools. The wood look tile welcomes you into the open floor plan of this split 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with a game room, and study or flex space for your family. The well-appointed kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop and vented wood surrounded hood giving it a custom feel. White cabinets with ample storage and a walk-in pantry completes this kitchen giving you all that you need for everyday life or the chef in you. Large utility room off the kitchen offers space for an extra referigerator or freezer.Light and bright, this home feels spacious and inviting for the ones that entertain.Lower electric bills with this energy efficient home.Seller offering up to $12,000 to help buy down rates which could bring it down as low as 5.5
